name: Frolicking Frog Licking
description:
Making a leaderboard proved to be a lot more difficult than I had expected,
so comment down below your highest score!

This game is about testing your reflexes as a hungry frog eating flies. 

How long can you survive before you let the poor frog starve to death?

This was a submission to the 'Finally Finish Something 2021' Game Jam.
Started this project back in August of 2018.
Been busy with work and school ever since and decided to finally finish it once and for all!
This is also my first officially published game and I hope you guys enjoy it!
